# WHO2RAID widget - Raid Randomizer (by [LeBluxTV](https://www.twitch.tv/lebluxtv))

## Description
Automatised Raid randomly choosen from streams you follow.

## Installation

```text

```

### Required files
- [OBS Shaderfilter 1.21 Plugin](https://github.com/Oncorporation/obs-shaderfilter)
- [OBS Websocket Plugin](https://obsproject.com/forum/resources/obs-websocket-remote-control-obs-studio-from-websockets.466/)

## Configuration

Don't forget **Set the directory of your OBS** in the `action`: WHO2RAID -> RAID RANDOMIZER FOLLOWED CURRENTLY LIVE -> !RaidWho<br>
Do the same for the WEBM File (video) 'TV SNOW'<br>
**In `Actions` named :**
WHO2RAID -> RAID RANDOMIZER FOLLOWED CURRENTLY LIVE -> !RaidWho
>You may need to set the entire path to your settings.json ( in streamer.bot's folder > data folder )
>in the Execute Code (line 342)
